abstract: Bio Kim, Kenrik Stenson and Justin Leonard share second-round lead at Children's Miracle Network golf tournament in Lake Buena Vista, Fla.
snippet: Henrik Stenson, Justin Leonard and the 21-year-old rookie Bio Kim were in a three-way tie for first at Disney in the final tournament of the year.
lead_paragraph: Henrik Stenson, Justin Leonard and the 21-year-old rookie Bio Kim were in a three-way tie for first at Disney in the final tournament of the year.
